Twisted-C++ 9.0.0

What is this?
=============

  Twisted-C++ is a port of Python Twisted, an event-based framework for 
  internet applications which works on Python 2.3 through 2.6.

Installing
==========

  Use CMake.

Unit Tests
==========


  Not implemented yet


Documentation and Support
=========================

  No documentation yet, but the aim is to be api-compatible with the Python
  version.

